                    temporibus ducimus. Perferendis, magnam.<br>
                <p class="price"><strong>Price : 50€</strong></p>
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="item">
                <img src="images/slider1.jpg" alt="barber">
                <h1>Smooth Shave </h1>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Totam libero minima eos recusandae atque
                    adipisci magni ducimus praesentium ipsum rem obcaecati,
                    nam earum blanditiis distinctio velit sequi temporibus numquam. Totam. <br>
                <p class="price"><strong>Price : 50€</strong></p>
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="item">
                <img src="images/slider1.jpg" alt="barber">
                <h1>Smooth Shave </h1>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Praesentium amet libero incidunt quis
                    fugiat ex at vel eaque repudiandae dolores dicta, tenetur laudantium dolore omnis aliquam
                    ea labore laborum quisquam? <br>
                <p class="price"><strong>Price : 50€</strong></p>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="divContainerBabers">
            <h1 id="barbers">Barbers</h1>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="item2">
                    <img class="barberimg" src="images/slider1.jpg" alt="barber">
                    <h1>Ahmad </h1>
                </div>

                <div class="item2">
                    <img src="images/slider1.jpg" alt="barber">
                    <h1>Sebastien </h1>
                </div>

                <div class="item2">
                    <img src="images/slider1.jpg" alt="barber">
                    <h1>Alex </h1>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <% if (typeof user!='undefined' ){%>
        <h1 id="contact">Contact</h1>
        <h3>You can send a message</h3>
            <div class="container">
                <form action="/index" method="POST">
                    <input type="text" name="fullname" value="<%=user.name %>" placeholder="full name">
                    <input type="text" name="email" value="<%= user.email %>" placeholder="email">
                    <p><textarea class="commentaireTextarea" name="message" cols="80" rows="10"> Message </textarea></p>
                    <button type="submit" class="myButton">Send a message  </button>
                </form>
            </div>
            <% }else{ %>
                <h1 id="contact">Contact</h1>
                <h3>To send a message you need to login</h3>
                <div class="container">
                    <form action="" method="POST">
                        <input type="text" name="fullname" id="inputForm" value="fullname" placeholder="full name">
                        <input type="text" name="email" id="inputForm" value="email" placeholder="email">
                        <p><textarea class="commentaireTextarea" id="textareaForm" name="message" cols="80"
                                rows="10"> Message </textarea></p>
                        <button type="submit" id="buttonForm" class="myButton">Send a message</button>
